WEBVTT

00:02:28.750 --> 00:02:33.434
than all of the planes, trains
and automobiles put together.

00:02:33.458 --> 00:02:36.934
And one third of our arable land is used

00:02:36.958 --> 00:02:39.309
to grow feed to feed
factory-farmed animals,

00:02:39.333 --> 00:02:40.976
rather than ourselves.

00:02:41.000 --> 00:02:44.934
And all that land is sprayed
with immeasurable chemicals.

00:02:44.958 --> 00:02:48.184
And ecologically important habitats,

00:02:48.208 --> 00:02:50.143
like the Amazon,

00:02:50.167 --> 00:02:52.601
are cut down and are burnt,

00:02:52.625 --> 00:02:56.143
all so we can feed
and house farmed animals.

00:02:56.167 --> 00:02:59.268
By the time my three kids grow up,

00:02:59.292 --> 00:03:02.059
